Package: pipedreams
Title: Pipe-Friendly Wrappers for Common Statistical Tests and Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Thulin", "Måns", email = "mans@statistikkonsult.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides data.frame S3 methods for common statistical functions
    (t.test, wilcox.test, lm, glm, aov) so that a data frame can be passed as
    the first argument via the base pipe (|>) without needing the placeholder
    syntax (data = _).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    survival,
    lme4,
    MASS
Config/testthat/edition: 3
